<div class="cat-thumbnail"><a href="http://www.101cookbooks.com/archives/lime-peanut-coleslaw-recipe.html"><img src="/mt-static/images/food/thumbnails/coleslaw_recipe.jpg" border="0" alt="Lime & Peanut Coleslaw" /></a></div>  
              <div class="cat-blurb"><a href="http://www.101cookbooks.com/archives/lime-peanut-coleslaw-recipe.html">Lime & Peanut Coleslaw</a><br />
<p>This feather-light, mayo-free, coleslaw recipe uses toasted peanuts, cherry tomatoes, and lime vinaigrette and is perfect alongside fajitas, or whatever you have coming off the grill. Keep in mind - great coleslaw is rooted in great knife skills. </p></div>
</div>
<br clear="all" /></div>



