   <div class="cat-holder">
<div class="cat-thumbnail"><a href="http://www.101cookbooks.com/archives/red-pesto-ravioli-recipe.html"><img src="/mt-static/images/food/thumbnails/red_pesto_ravioli.jpg" border="0" alt="Red Pesto Ravioli" /></a></div>
              
              <div class="cat-blurb"><a href="http://www.101cookbooks.com/archives/red-pesto-ravioli-recipe.html">Red Pesto Ravioli</a><br />
<p>For the sun-dried tomato lovers out there. Goat-cheese raviolis tossed in a sun-dried tomato red pesto sauce, served over baby spinach.</p></div>
</div>
