<p>So so so yummy. I like my meals rich and hearty so i added a bit more cream. Also I would probably lessen the amount of olive oil next time, but i LOVED how creamy and soft and spicy this was! It was perfect with chicken sausage and a simple salad with shredded asiago, walnuts and balsamic. </p>

<p>YUM!</p></div></div>
